.TH ND300 1 "April 2026" "shaughvOS" "QubeTX 300 Series"
.SH NAME
nd300 \- QubeTX network diagnostics (ND-300)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nd300
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B nd300
is the QubeTX ND-300 Network Diagnostic. In user mode it runs
eight core network checks covering connectivity, DNS, and latency.
.PP
With
.B \-t
(technician mode),
.B nd300
expands to 17 deep diagnostics including DNS resolution paths,
gateway reachability, packet loss, MTU probing, and bufferbloat.
The ND-300 package ships alongside
.BR speedqx (1),
a quad-provider speed test.
.SH OPTIONS
See
.B nd300 \-\-help
for the full list of flags and modes.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shaughvos (1),
.BR tr300 (1),
.BR sd300 (1),
.BR speedqx (1)
